front.title: •3B3-10
front.gametext: While at Theed Palace Hallway, opponent's characters may not move from here. Once per game may take Halt! Into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
front.lore: Infantry battle droid who assumed command after his regiment's commander fell to Amidala's blaster. Re-routed Droid Control Ship order to himself in the heat of battle.
